ent. Hooker-line burials at Mt. Hope: George Cooley Gordon Sr (X02281), Ida May Hooker Gordon (H03892, with monument), William 'Willie' Gordon (HD3268), George Cooley Gordon II (HD3262), Cecelia Mitchell Kimball Gordon (X02282), George Cooley Gordon III (HD3263), Cornelia Macy Hawks Gordon (X02283), Cecilia 'Trottie' Gordon (HD3264), Laura Kimball Gordon (HD3265), Fred Hooker Gordon Sr (HD3266) with separate Section MM Lot 266 plot, Florence Robinson Gordon (X02284), Fred Hooker Gordon Jr (HD-prefix), Virginia DeVilbiss Gordon (X-prefix), Fred Hooker Gordon III (HD-prefix, infant Boston meningioma), Lucius Robinson 'Bob' Gordon (HD-prefix, NOTABLE), Marie Antoinette 'Tony' Townson Gordon (X-prefix), William Ward Gordon (HD-prefix), Emilie Wolcott Gordon (X-prefix), William Ward Gordon Jr (HD-prefix back in original Lot 61 Range 2). Largest Hooker-tree concentration after Cypress Lawn SF.","hooker_connections":["H03434","H03437","H03892","HD3261","HD3262","HD3263","HD3264","HD3265","HD3266","HD3267","HD3268","HD3275","HD3276","HD3277","HD3279","HD3280","HD3400","HD3401","HD3834","HD3836","HD3842","I00339","X02281","X02282","X02283","X02284","X02290","X02293","X02295","HD3870","HD3871","HD3872","HD3873","HD3874","HD3875","I00490","I00491","I00492","I00494","X03270","X03271","X03272","X03273","X03274"],"person_ids":["HD3870","HD3871","HD3872","HD3873","HD3874","HD3875","I00490","I00491","I00492","I00494"]},"institutionsById":{},"crossConnections":[]}